      "asbval:note": "The paper is a primary research article describing NP Analyst platform development and validation. It does not discuss or demonstrate a meta-level skill for preparing articles for expert review, indexing tools, or gap detection in other papers. The research_question describes a methodological skill/workflow that is not the subject of this paper.",
